178
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,039
I like eunuchs.

179
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:48,480
You like eunuchs?

180
00:09:49,799 --> 00:09:51,039
So that's Your Majesty's taste.

181
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,720
But what should we do?

182
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,919
A distant water
can't quench a nearby thirst.

183
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:58,480
Let me be the one
to relieve your aphrodisiac.

184
00:10:00,639 --> 00:10:01,639
Aphrodisiac?

185
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:02,759
What aphrodisiac?

186
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:04,279
Your Majesty,

187
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,679
consent to me.

188
00:10:06,799 --> 00:10:07,919
What did you give me?

189
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,519
Your Majesty, rest assured.

190
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:10,879
It's just something

191
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,879
to bring us joy tonight.

192
00:10:16,639 --> 00:10:17,639
Your Majesty,

193
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:18,919
