194
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,600
Give in to me.

195
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,120
Okay?

196
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,919
Master Pei,

197
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,240
